document_data.name: Neville Dobbin
document_data.mainbody: '''Earl Neville Dobbin''' was the 35{{th}} earl of [[Stagwick]] in [[Hartsvale]]. He was known as the author of ''[[A Full History of the Dobbins of Stagwick]]''. [[Ruther Dobbin]] was one of his descendants.
